quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,103,"“Ndithu tikudziwa kuti iwo akunena: “Pali munthu amene akumphunzitsa.” (Koma) chiyankhulo cha amene akumganizirayo nchachilendo, ndipo ichi (chiyankhulo cha Qur’an) ndi chiyankhulo cha Chiarabu chomveka"
  16,104,"“Ndithudi amene sakhulupirira Ayah (ndime) za Allah, Allah sawaongolera (kunjira ya choonadi), choncho adzapeza chilango chowawa"
  16,105,“Ndithudi amene sakhulupirira Ayah (ndime) za Allah ndi amene amapeka bodza (ndi kumalifalitsa kwa anthu) ndipo iwowo ndiwo onama
  16,106,"“Amene akukana Allah, pambuyo pomukhulupirira, (chilango chachikulu chikumuyembekezera), kupatula yemwe adakakamizidwa, uku mtima wake utakhazikika pa chikhulupiliro; koma amene akutsekulira mtima wake kusakhulupirira, mkwiyo wa Allah uli pa iwo (ndipo anthu otere) adzapata chilango chachikulu"
  16,107,“Zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti iwo adakonda moyo wa dziko lapansi kwambiri kuposa wa pambuyo pa imfa; ndi kutinso Allah saongola anthu osakhulupirira
  16,108,"“Iwo ndi omwe Allah adawadinda m’mitima mwawo, m’makutu mwawo, ndi m’maso mwawo (chifukwa cha kusimbwa kwawo). Ndipo iwo ngonyalanyaza (malamulo a Allah) kwambiri"
  16,109,“Palibe chikaiko chakuti iwo ngotaika kwambiri pa tsiku la chimaliziro
  16,110,"“Ndithudi kenako Mbuye wako, kwa amene adasamuka pambuyo pakusautsidwa (kufikira adanena zosayenera) komanso nkuchita Jihâd ndikupirira (chifukwa cha chipembedzo), ndithu Mbuye wako pambuyo pa zimenezo, Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosantha"